<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title> 게시글 상세보기 </title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #f0fff4;
        }

        .custom-card {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 1000px;
            min-height: 500px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 30px;
            margin-top: 60px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(40, 167, 69, 0.2);
        }

        .text-primary {
            color: #28a745 !important;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background-color: #28a745;
            border-color: #28a745;
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            background-color: #218838;
            border-color: #1e7e34;
        }

        .table th {
            width: 100px;
            background-color: #e9f7ef;
        }

        .btn-warning {
            background-color: #ffc107;
            border-color: #ffc107;
        }

        .btn-warning:hover {
            background-color: #e0a800;
            border-color: #d39e00;
        }

        .btn-danger {
            background-color: #dc3545;
            border-color: #dc3545;
        }

        .btn-danger:hover {
            background-color: #c82333;
            border-color: #bd2130;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container d-flex flex-column align-items-center">
    <div class="custom-card">
        <h2 class="fw-bold text-primary mb-4 text-center">글 상세보기</h2>
        <table class="table table-bordered mb-4">
            <tbody>
            <tr>
                <th scope="row">제목</th>
                <td>{{menus.title}}</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <th scope="row">설명</th>
                <td style="white-space: pre-wrap;">{{menus.content}}</td>
            </tr>
            </tbody>
        </table>
        <div class="d-flex justify-content-end">
            <a href="/menus" class="btn btn-primary me-2">목록으로</a>
            <a href="/menus/{{menus.id}}/edit" class="btn btn-warning me-2">수정</a>
            <a href="/menus/{{menus.id}}/delete" class="btn btn-danger"
               onclick="return confirm('삭제하시겠습니까?');">삭제</a>
        </div>

        <br>
        <div class="mt-4">
            <h4 class="text-primary">댓글 목록</h4>
            {{#commentList}}
                <div class="card mb-2">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <p class="card-text" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">{{text}}</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            {{/commentList}}
            {{^commentList}}
                <p>아직 등록된 댓글이 없습니다. 첫 댓글을 남겨주세요!</p>
            {{/commentList}}
        </div>
        <br>

        <!-- 댓글 작성 폼 (이전과 동일) -->
        <div class="card mb-3">
            <div class="card-body">
                <form action="/menus/{{id}}/comments" method="post">
                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <label for="commentContent" class="form-label">댓글 내용</label>
                        <textarea class="form-control form-control-sm" id="commentContent" name="text" rows="3" required></textarea>
                    </div>
                    <div class="text-end">
                        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm">댓글 등록</button>
                    </div>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>


    </div>

</body>
</html>